OL,4,G2000FAgony
OL,5,     GJane is in despair about her
OL,6,     Gmarriage to Laurence and refuses
OL,7,     Gto see him or allow him into
OL,8,     Gtheir flat. Laurence bribes Bea
OL,9,     Ginto inviting him to Jane's
OL,10,     Gforthcoming New Year's Eve party.
OL,11,G2030FSecond Thoughts
OL,12,     GFaith and Bill spend a night away
OL,13,     Gfrom home in a nearby hotel in
OL,14,     Gthe hope of a romantic break.
OL,15,G2100FDrop The Dead Donkey
OL,16,     GGus decides that Globelink is
OL,17,     Gsuffering from 'team-unbonding'.
